 ~/     206 - mixed light industrial - single occupancy (condo) (ITE 110)
 ~/     207 - research and development (ITE 760)
 mo01
 +((0.75)*(mo76/1000)*(0.47)*((mo77.ge.200)*(mo77.le.204))
 +(0.98)*(mo76/1000)*(0.88)*((mo77.ge.205)*(mo77.le.206))
 +(1.07)*(mo76/1000)*(0.85)*(mo77.eq.207))*(mo07)

                 /constraint matrix
 n              /no submatrix
